c: 28
v: 82
t: Ureueng nyang napsu lagee jih baroe Jikheun treuk jinoe ceulaka leupah Keubit cit Tuhan Neujok raseuki Keu soe nyang Neubri roe nyang h‘eut Allah Ladom keu hamba-Neuh hana Neubri Adak meu Neubri ceulaka sudah Adak kon rahmat Neubri le Tuhan Tanyoe pih meunan sit keunong teulah Teuntee meutanom tanyoe lam bumoe Adak kon tanyoe na rahmat Allah Hana bahgia keubit soe kaphe